    "In 2022-2024, significant strides were made in the field of generative models, enabling computers to interact with natural language more effectively and understand users' creative processes.",
    "This has ushered in new possibilities for computers to assist users in creating images, videos, and audio in ways that surpass the capabilities of traditional tools."
